tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE art_supplies (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255),
    category VARCHAR(100),
    stock_quantity INT,
    price DECIMAL(10, 2)
);

CREATE TABLE art_supplies (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
  type VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
  brand VARCHAR(100),
  price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE supply_inventory (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  supply_id INT NOT NULL,
  quantity INT NOT NULL,
  location VARCHAR(255),
  FOREIGN KEY (supply_id) REFERENCES art_supplies(id)
);
